Buy her something.

596
00:41:14,820 --> 00:41:16,019
A bag,

597
00:41:16,019 --> 00:41:17,059
makeup, whatever.

598
00:41:17,579 --> 00:41:18,219
Coax her

599
00:41:18,340 --> 00:41:19,000
at my best.

600
00:41:20,079 --> 00:41:21,679
Miao Jing doesn't care about that stuff.

601
00:41:23,099 --> 00:41:23,860
Besides,

602
00:41:25,320 --> 00:41:26,320
my taste is terrible.

603
00:41:27,420 --> 00:41:28,380
It's not about money.

604
00:41:30,360 --> 00:41:31,119
It's about

605
00:41:31,500 --> 00:41:32,280
being humble

606
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:33,219
and submissive,

607
00:41:33,699 --> 00:41:34,079
see?

608
00:41:35,619 --> 00:41:35,980
Who?

609
00:41:36,480 --> 00:41:37,619
Giving lectures?

610
00:41:37,619 --> 00:41:38,079
Well,

611
00:41:38,380 --> 00:41:38,900
I'm teaching him...

612
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:40,739
Yi, don't listen to him.

613
00:41:40,980 --> 00:41:41,820
Come for dinner?

614
00:41:41,820 --> 00:41:42,559
Food's ready.

615
00:41:42,739 --> 00:41:43,119
Yeah.

616
00:41:43,119 --> 00:41:43,519
Okay.
